---
title: One-pot Chorizo and Mozzarella Orzo	 with creme fraiche and fresh sage
description: What's better than a one-pot dish? Less mess, less stress,  with full-on flavour, this chorizo and mozzarella orzo is creamy, lightly spiced, and hearty like a hug in a bowl.
